/pdshhd{/x 2 index def/y 1 index def dsh0
		.7 SLW x y M
0 3 RM 1 SLW 
		4.25 -3 rlineto
		-4.25 -3 rlineto
		-4.25 3 rlineto
		closepath stroke}!
/pshhd{/x 2 index def/y 1 index def dsh0
